# Student Performance Analysis

## Project Overview
This project analyzes student performance data using Excel.

## Dataset Features
- Gender
- Race/Ethnicity
- Parental Level of Education
- Lunch Type
- Test Preparation
- Math Score
- Reading Score
- Writing Score

## Tools Used
- Microsoft Excel
- Data Visualization

## Key Findings
- Student scores vary across parental education levels.
- Reading and writing scores are generally higher than math scores.
- Test preparation appears to improve performance.

